      "content": "it just feels so heavy. i look at him stuff, his books, his clothes... and i just feel like i'm trespassing in a life that's already over. everything is just a reminder of what i lost. i feel like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever will. it's like i'm just stuck in this waiting room for a life that's already ended.",
